	<h3 class="title"><a href="/279191#comment-3010964" class="active">Mandatory drug testing</a></h3>
    <div class="submitted active">Submitted by <a href="/user/45845" title="View user profile.">Jungleboogie</a> on Fri, 03/22/2013 - 19:01.  <a class="permalink" href="/comment/3010964">Permalink</a></div>
	<div class="content">
     <p>Is one of the most common sense rules ever created.  I work in the oil industry, and drug testing is pretty much standard all over.  I am quite happy about that - who wants to be looking over their shoulder worrying about some drugged up idiot in a backhoe, driving a truck or on a pile driver or crane?</p>
<p>There are enough idiots to worry about as there is.</p>
